  "text": "In previous studies, we have demonstrated that a specific composition of ECM fulfils a regulatory role on the bronchial branching in chick embryos. This ECM composition shows a peculiar spatialtemporal distribution at the bronchial level during development [CITATION_1] . Therefore, it is clear that ECM remodelling processes play an important morphogenetic role. In this respect, it",
